Final Project
=============

1. a daemon
2. read rooms.dat
3. create a fifo for each room name
   (all lowercase, remove whitespace, suffix fifo)
4. open named pipes
5. Read schedule.dat
6. 


Thermostat Protocol
-------------------

daemon      pipe
~~~~~~      ~~~~
Q           XXX Q OK\n
H           H OK\n
C           C OK\n

XXX is room temp

69-74 degrees when occupied
50-92 degrees when not
